one_reviews_text:
It's alright. YOu're playing Frogger but you are the frog. Hop across roads forever.


Made me very, very nauseous.

Ever wondered what it would be like to be the frog in frogger?  Wonder no more!  Seriously, you will laugh when you see a bus coming right at you and *splat*.   You still get that feeling of horror and then laugh when you realize, it's not real.  Let's try that again :D

review_title: the most fun i've had playing in traffic
one_reviews_text: hay im walkin here.... said my girlfriend... JK i dont have a girlfried, but dont neeed one thanks to this fun time game. I have 2 cats now.
Fun game. Simple, addictive and replayable. The streets are generated at random and the leaderboard gives the game a bit of purpose.
Simple graphics, mildly addictive, street crossing game through busier and busier traffic until the inevitable happens.
A fun little game for a short while but it gets repetitive quickly and is one of the few games that makes me feel nauseous after a few minutes.
Very simple street crossing game. Graphics are very nice and the game is relaxing and addicting. Liked it a lot
